item.title: Compile Errors~PLZZ HELP!
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

Looks like you didnt add a “}” before that first error. check just before the first line of errors and make sure there is a “}” before it. otherwise it thinks its a code along with the code previous to it…

and if thats not it, make sure your not in an area that needs a “break;” after the codes. If thats it, then u might not have the “break;” at the end of the last code, before the first line of error in that
